## chat-app
A simple real-time chat app using Node.js and Socket.IO. You can open it in two tabs and chat with each other instantly.

## Installation
Clone the repository and install dependencies:
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Muhammad-Yaqoob-4110/we-chat.git
```
```
cd node-server
```
```
npm install
```

## Run the Backend
```bash
node index.js
```
It will show: Server is started on port 8000! Go and talk with your friend.

## Run the Frontend
Go live with the `index.html` file located in the main directory. You can use Live Server in VS Code. Open the link in two tab of your browser and start chatting!

